# DTS Architecture Principles (架构原则)

Scope: all DTS projects under `/opt/prod/dts/rdc`

## Three-Language Architecture (三语言架构)

- Python: AI Core only (Agent, Intent, RAG, Skill execution, evaluation, scheduling, observability)
- Java: Business Platform only (CRUD, RBAC, Keycloak, Ontology storage, governance, workflow, audit)
- Go: Infrastructure only (K8s Operator, CLI, deployment orchestration)
- Do NOT mix responsibilities across language boundaries.
- Python services are enhancement layers — Java services must function independently without them.

## Communication (通信)

- Control plane (synchronous): gRPC between all services.
- Data plane (asynchronous): Kafka KRaft for CDC, event streams, audit, and Pack data channels.
- Frontend to backend: REST via dts-gateway (with gRPC-Web translation where needed).
- All inter-service calls must carry JWT user context for permission verification.

## Storage (存储)

- PostgreSQL: primary relational store (Ontology metadata, business data, permissions).
- ClickHouse: time-series and analytical queries (MES/SCADA, audit wide tables).
- Neo4j CE: graph relationships (lineage, impact chains). Abstract via GraphStore interface for NebulaGraph switch.
- pgvector: vector index (RAG, semantic search). Abstract via VectorStore interface for Milvus switch.
- MinIO: object storage (files, models, offline bundles).
- Kafka KRaft: messaging, event streaming, CDC. No ZooKeeper.

## Deployment (部署)

- All-in-K8s: single architecture for online and offline. No degraded mode.
- All middleware (PG, Kafka, ClickHouse, Neo4j, MinIO) deployed inside K8s by default.
- Support external instances via Helm values configuration.
- Online vs offline difference: ONLY LLM endpoint and image registry source.
- Four scenarios: dev single-node / small offline / mid-size cluster / cloud.

## Authentication (认证)

- Keycloak for identity (OIDC/SAML/PKI).
- JWT token propagation between services (no mTLS).
- dts-gateway enforces authentication on ALL incoming requests.

## Observability (可观测性)

- OpenTelemetry SDK in all services (Python/Java/Go).
- Grafana Tempo for distributed tracing.
- Prometheus for metrics.
- Grafana Loki for logs.
- Grafana for unified dashboards.
- Single traceId links infrastructure traces and AI execution traces.

## Frontend (前端)

- React 19 + Vite + shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS.
- Three separate apps: admin (ops), cortex (analyst), pilot (decision-maker).
- Additional libraries: Vercel AI SDK, React Flow, @dnd-kit.
- Each app is a static SPA served by nginx. No SSR/Node runtime required.
